** MSG,
ENTER DATE!
DATE IS NOT IN CALENDAR MASTER!
DATE DOES NOT FIND IN KANBAN MASTER!
SHIFT SHOULD BE 1, 2 OR 3!
COPIES SHOULD BE GREATER THAN 1 AND LESS THAN 10
PRINTER OPTION SHOULD BE 1 - 7 OR BLANK!
LIST TYPE SBOULD BE 1 OR BLANK!
PRESS F5 TO PRINT, OR F3 TO EXIT...

